I have several on my shelf that are broken and closed. I squirt them
with paint so I don't attempt to use them for anything else other than
setting up the thermostat bracket. The expanded ones I have I was real
lucky with, they expanded and stayed captive in the bracket and the
flaps were forced to stay open.

